{"tid":2411792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅蘭妮亞不忍了！斥責CNN散布她的假消息","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T17:18:23.000Z","uid":75656,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9adf094a47419c8c945d42822dff14ce5042f8","tid":2411792,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）12日引述「不具名」消息人士報導，前第一夫人梅蘭妮亞（MelaniaTrump）對於現任第一夫人吉兒（Jill Biden）獲得媒體一致好評，心裡不是滋味，十分眼紅，所以成立個人辦公室一別苗頭。對此，梅蘭妮亞罕見作出回擊，強調她已是普通公民，CNN仍然熱衷於散布關於她的虛假小道消息，傳播負面新聞，該做法是一種「不健康的嗜好」。<br />\n<br />\n相較於吉兒受美國主流媒體呵護追捧，梅蘭妮亞2017年當上美國第一夫人後，從說話腔調到服飾，往往遭到CNN等主流媒體嘲笑，甚至川普卸任後，仍不放過。<br />\n<br />\nCNN駐白宮記者貝內特（Kate Bennett）在報導中稱，梅蘭妮亞11日在推特宣布個人辦公室正式開張運作，似有意證明自己有所作為，要跟吉兒一別苗頭。<br />\n<br />\n報導還引述不具名消息人士說法，繪聲繪影地指稱，自從梅蘭妮亞上月隨川普卸任返回佛州私人莊園「海湖俱樂部」（Mar-a-lago）後，就一直過著悠閒生活，「她去做spa，吃午餐，然後（再）去做spa，晚上再跟川普吃晚餐。」<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，「有別於她丈夫，前第一夫人已經差不多把華府的時光拋諸腦後」。<br />\n<br />\n梅蘭妮亞辦公室14日在其推特發文說：「梅蘭妮亞已經不再是第一夫人了，現在是一位普通公民，一位母親和妻子，這篇文章的消息人士與她沒有任何關係，對於她的個人生活和思想一點都不了解，但是CNN卻選擇發布了一個虛假的小道消息，這個報導表明了美國媒體不健康地報導梅蘭妮亞負面消息的嗜好。」<br />\n<br />\n梅蘭妮亞辦公室還轉推了「女性挺川普」（Women for Trump）組織發起人克萊默（Amy Kremer）在推特上的推文，推文中質問：「華府的記者貝內特為何要在梅蘭妮亞已經離開白宮，並準備作為一位普通公民生活時，寫一篇攻擊她的文章？」，文中並敦促美國主流媒體應通情達理，讓梅蘭妮亞過自己的生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440804&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN279ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=85c94b1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440804&h=53c8147e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440804</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AmyKremer/status/1360604567499649026?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmyKremer%2Fstatus%2F1360604567499649026%3Fs%3D20&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN279ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=af764b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmyKremer%2Fstatus%2F1360604567499649026%3Fs%3D20&h=3766ead1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AmyKremer/status/1360604567499649026?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/OfficeofMelania/status/1360660122394128391?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOfficeofMelania%2Fstatus%2F1360660122394128391%3Fs%3D20&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN279ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=97a5c788\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOfficeofMelania%2Fstatus%2F1360660122394128391%3Fs%3D20&h=5043e5ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/OfficeofMelania/status/1360660122394128391?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"f8bb9bce9352311eda8a2e48460d283ab65975b4","tid":2411792,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a000292b35829c099fad0223f6cadca434e38452","tid":2411792,"uid":70238,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"Cause CNN has learnt from 連登：禍必及家人。"},{"pid":"777006f45ddfa7c0f0d807f805a425b9cf69f982","tid":2411792,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785cacd90d4cac244cbda5e91092eb03501fc972","tid":2411792,"uid":